title: QUEEN + Adam LAMBERT - Live in Moscow 2012
description:
Description: The only concert in Moscow greatest group QUEEN with Adam Lambert as a vocalist in the short tour of six performances in 2012. From the perspective of video quality is of interest for the true fans and connoisseurs, as a group QUEEN, and Adam Lambert. 

Extras. Information: Survey was conducted without interruption from the balcony of the sports complex "Olympic" in Moscow camcorder SONY HDR-CX580EV autotuning.

SETLIST:

01. Seven Seas of Rhye
02. Keep Yourself Alive
03. We Will Rock You
04. Fat Bottomed Girls
05. Don't Stop Me Now
06. Under Pressure (vocals Roger Taylor & Adam Lambert)
07. I Want It All
08. Who Wants to Live Forever
09. A Kind of Magic (vocals Roger Taylor)
10. These Are the Days of Our Lives (vocals Roger Taylor)
11. Life is Real (Song for Lennon) (sung by Zemfira Ramzanova; Keyboards by Dmitry; acoustic guitar Brian May)
12. Love of My Life (vocals Brian May)
13. '39 (vocals Brian May & Roger Taylor)
14. Dragon Attack (including bass solo)
15. Drum Solo
16. Guitar Solo
17. I Want to Break Free
18. Another One Bites the Dust
19. Radio Ga Ga
20. Somebody to Love
21. Crazy Little Thing Called Love
22. The Show Must Go On
23. Bohemian Rhapsody

Encore:
24. Tie Your Mother Down (vocals Brian May)
25. We Will Rock You
26. We Are the Champions

Brian May - guitar, vocals
Roger Taylor - drums, vocals
+
Adam Lambert - vocals
+
Rufus Tiger Taylor - drums & percussion
